title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 8 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 8 2021
description:
Why Joe Biden's numbers continue to plummet. Big Bird and his grandma participate in a CNN Town Hall on vaccines. Yes, the Sesame Street character. Wisconsin Senator Ron Johnson weighs in on the border, vaccine mandates and Aaron Rodgers -- and how everything adds up to social control. Florida Senator Rick Scott nails CNN on their flimsy and misleading reporting about CRT.
